item.title: CVE-2022-23766|2024-08-03T03:51:45.993Z -- bluetree%20co.%2C%20ltd -- bigfileagent
item.description: An improper input validation vulnerability leading to arbitrary file execution was discovered in BigFileAgent. In order to cause arbitrary files to be executed, the attacker makes the victim access a web page d by them or inserts a script using XSS into a general website.
